data.eml:eml: A taxonomic study on the species of the genus Diestramima Storozhenko (Orthoptera: Rhaphidophoridae, Aemodogryllinae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Qin, Yanyan, Wang, Hanqiang, Liu, Xianwei, Li, Kai (2016): A taxonomic study on the species of the genus Diestramima Storozhenko (Orthoptera: Rhaphidophoridae, Aemodogryllinae). Zootaxa 4126 (4): 514-532, DOI: http://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4126.4.4
